summary: I created a new spell called the force of nature. It\'s a damage spell that deals 125 health and stamina damage.
descriptionHtml:
Please note that it\'s still in an early beta phase and I plan to add new spells and abilities for warrior\'s and rogues.

You can buy the spell from the Riverwood trader!

I also need help with this spell, if anyone knows how to retexture a spell/shader please contact me and help me out! :)

Video will be uploaded as soon as I can!
author: Passet
